              <span>Logs disappear on page reload</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-red-400 flex-shrink-0">‚Üí</span>
              <span>Can't correlate console errors with network failures</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-red-400 flex-shrink-0">‚Üí</span>
              <span>Debugging across multiple tabs is a nightmare</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-red-400 flex-shrink-0">‚Üí</span>
              <span>No way to query historical logs</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-red-400 flex-shrink-0">‚Üí</span>
              <span>DevTools sends data to cloud services (Sentry, etc)</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Solution side -->
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-emerald-400">‚úÖ Browser Logger</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-300">
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-emerald-400 flex-shrink-0">‚Üí</span>
