        </div>

        <!-- Feature 2 -->
        <div class="p-6 border border-gray-800 rounded-lg hover:border-emerald-500/50 transition-smooth glow-box">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-4">üåê</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Network Monitoring</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">Full request/response breakdown including DNS, connect, SSL, send, wait, and receive timing. Identify slow endpoints instantly.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature 3 -->
        <div class="p-6 border border-gray-800 rounded-lg hover:border-emerald-500/50 transition-smooth glow-box">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-4">üíæ</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">SQLite Storage</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">All logs in a queryable database. Use powerful SQL to find exactly what you're looking for. No cloud required.</p>
        </div>

